Pick n Pay Opens Second Zambia Store, Plans Five More Over Next Four Years

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-28T07:28:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/pick-n-pay-opens-second-zambia-store-plans-five-more-over-next-four-years.html
Pick n Pay Stores Ltd. (PIK)  said it
opened its second store in Zambia and plans another five in the
southern African country over the next four years.  The Cape Town-based grocery chain commented in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  